=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國就ABC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n端傳媒都紅紅地"},{"pid":"f0a60304077dd3649f3cdf5e0e500841d75942e9","tid":231170,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>普通市民都係靠支共放料㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為唔係紅底所以咩料都收唔到，睇條毛？</blockquote><br />\n冇人話唔睇<br />\n<br />\n不過唔好學黃屍別share 完以為自己民主豆豉囉</blockquote><br />\n無衝突<br />\n你睇紅媒唔代表反民主<br />\n但如果你係港獨派走去share就有啲衝突啦<br />\n不過都係嗰句，根本要收支共料就要紅底埋堆，你局外人根本咩都唔知<br />\n你又要睇支共嘅嘢，又要貞節牌坊<br />\n除非你立心唔睇支共料，唔睇支共係香港做過咩衰嘢，做個唔理身邊時勢，只係一味鳩衝嘅港獨士兵。冇問題，一定要有爛頭卒，但我唔係，好多人都唔會做"},{"pid":"58b3f1d2fbf0c6f64515ab36535a5b85eb406d5d","tid":231170,"uid":21772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傳真社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />端傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國就ABC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賊媒01有得睇既野佢地有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde2137a0f0b4bba28e0069c01f488a962fb9959","tid":231170,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"聚言時報"},{"pid":"c14dc093d5dc4f414dbd7b8979b500e6a56910ed","tid":231170,"uid":1495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本土新聞, 傳真社, 關鍵評論網(有得睇哲學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</blockquote><br />\n關鍵成日出返啲舊文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b644a6156ac101b3310f529a2902ea9f462626","tid":231170,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>傳真社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree